This is the Azure 0.1.

What Azure is
------------
Azure is a featherweight yet powerful language designed for both embedding
and stand-alone purposes. Azure is compact and requires little resource.
It is written in ANSI C, and compiles on many common platforms. It has many
useful features like dynamic typing and garbage collection. For a detailed
description of Azure, refer to the documents in the doc directory. Azure is
very young and still under rapid development, please keep a close eye on the
next release for more exciting new features!


Installation
------------
Azure can be easily installed on different platforms. For the information of a
specific platform, please refer to INSTALL in the same directory.

Contacting the authors
------------
Azure's authors welcome any constructive suggestions, criticisms, and bug
reports. The authors can be reached at azure.lang@gmail.com.